  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Background
    This is a background monitor for the application that runs hourly to monitor data inside the MetaDataB database.

    This database is a non-encrypted database containing non-vital information that's purely for monitoring chunk metas to find out if and when we should schedule an update as to where they are storedx Created by Spencer on 3/29/2016.
